*Vino* je obavezno uz svaki ručak. (Wine is mandatory with every lunch.)

Moj otac pije *vinom* svakog dana. (My father drinks wine every day.)

Ona voli da uživa u *vinu*. (She likes to enjoy wine.)

On je pio *vinu* preko noći. (He drank wine all night.)

Njegov omiljeni *vin* je crveno. (His favorite wine is red.)